Privacy Policy for Yoga Mudras

Last Updated: May 23, 2024

Yoga Mudras (the "App") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of information through our mobile application.

1. Information Collection and Use
Yoga Mudras does not collect, store, or share any personal information.
Offline Functionality: The App is designed to function entirely offline.
Local Data: Any data created during your use of the App (such as "Favorite" mudras or timer preferences) is stored locally on your device only. We do not have access to this data.
No Accounts: You are not required to create an account or provide an email address to use the App.

2. Third-Party Services
The App does not use any third-party analytics, advertising networks, or tracking tools that collect user data.

3. Permissions
The App may request the following permissions for specific features:
Vibration: To provide haptic feedback when the practice timer starts or ends.
Audio/Sound: To play system tones when a session is complete. These permissions are used solely to enhance the user experience and do not involve data collection.

4. Children’s Privacy
Since we do not collect any personal information, our App does not knowingly collect any data from children.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at: Email: rselvaguru@gmail.com
